text: Hüseyin Gürsoy (born 1932) is a Turkish wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle 87 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:Living people Category:Turkish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Turkey Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from Oltu
